<p class="ql-align-justify">风摇树筛下日光</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一根老冰棍</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">透着青春的忧伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那爱写诗的少女</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">夹一本日记</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">走过石板街</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">长长的裙裾</p>
